{"id": "art-493", "label": "Art. 493", "title": "Art. 493: Măsurile preventive", "slug": "art-493", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 493: M&#259;surile preventive </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1218006647\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1279\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1218006647\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Judec&#259;torul\nde drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i, în cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, la\npropunerea procurorului, sau, dup&#259; caz, judec&#259;torul de camer&#259;\npreliminar&#259; ori instan&#355;a poate dispune, dac&#259; exist&#259; motive\ntemeinice care justific&#259; suspiciunea rezonabil&#259; c&#259; persoana\njuridic&#259; a s&#259;vâr&#351;it o fapt&#259; prev&#259;zut&#259; de legea\npenal&#259; &#351;i numai pentru a se asigura buna desf&#259;&#351;urare a\nprocesului penal, una sau mai multe dintre urm&#259;toarele m&#259;suri:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_600107538\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1278\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_600107538\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>interdic&#355;ia\nini&#355;ierii ori, dup&#259; caz, suspendarea procedurii de dizolvare sau\nlichidare a persoanei juridice;</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) Prin Decizia RIL nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>18/2020</span><span style='color:black'>, ICCJ admite\nrecursul în interesul legii formulat de procurorul general al Parchetului de pe\nlâng&#259; Înalta Curte de Casa&#355;ie &#351;i Justi&#355;ie &#351;i în\ninterpretarea &#351;i aplicarea unitar&#259; a dispozi&#355;iilor art. 493\nalin. (1) lit. a) din Codul de procedur&#259; penal&#259; stabile&#351;te:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>&quot;Interdic&#355;ia ini&#355;ierii ori, dup&#259; caz, suspendarea\nprocedurii de dizolvare sau lichidare a persoanei juridice nu vizeaz&#259;\n&#351;i dizolvarea, respectiv lichidarea în procedura falimentului\nprev&#259;zut&#259; de Legea nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>85/2014</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind procedurile de prevenire a insolven&#355;ei\n&#351;i de insolven&#355;&#259;.&quot;</span></b><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_390175074\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1277\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_390175074\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)interdic&#355;ia ini&#355;ierii ori, dup&#259; caz,\nsuspendarea fuziunii, a diviz&#259;rii sau a reducerii capitalului social al\npersoanei juridice, început&#259; anterior sau în cursul urm&#259;ririi penale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1949359894\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1276\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1949359894\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)interzicerea unor opera&#355;iuni patrimoniale,\nsusceptibile de a antrena diminuarea activului patrimonial sau insolven&#355;a\npersoanei juridice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_324535114\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1275\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_324535114\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)interzicerea încheierii anumitor acte juridice, stabilite\nde organul judiciar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1672117697\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1274\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1672117697\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)interzicerea desf&#259;&#351;ur&#259;rii\nactivit&#259;&#355;ilor de natura celor cu ocazia c&#259;rora a fost\ncomis&#259; infrac&#355;iunea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2128273131\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1273\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2128273131\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Pentru a asigura respectarea m&#259;surilor\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1), persoana juridic&#259; poate fi obligat&#259; la\ndepunerea unei cau&#355;iuni constând într-o sum&#259; de bani care nu poate fi\nmai mic&#259; de 10.000 lei. Cau&#355;iunea se restituie la data r&#259;mânerii\ndefinitive a hot&#259;rârii de condamnare, de amânare a aplic&#259;rii\npedepsei, de renun&#355;are la aplicarea pedepsei sau de încetare a procesului\npenal, pronun&#355;ate în cauz&#259;, dac&#259; persoana juridic&#259; a respectat\nm&#259;sura sau m&#259;surile preventive, precum &#351;i în cazul în care, prin\nhot&#259;râre definitiv&#259;, s-a dispus achitarea persoanei juridice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2023139166\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1272\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2023139166\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cau&#355;iunea nu se restituie în cazul\nnerespect&#259;rii de c&#259;tre persoana juridic&#259; a m&#259;surii sau a\nm&#259;surilor preventive luate, f&#259;cându-se venit la bugetul de stat la\ndata r&#259;mânerii definitive a hot&#259;rârii pronun&#355;ate în cauz&#259;,\nprecum &#351;i dac&#259; s-a dispus plata din cau&#355;iune, în ordinea\nurm&#259;toare, a desp&#259;gubirilor b&#259;ne&#351;ti acordate pentru\nrepararea pagubelor cauzate de infrac&#355;iune, a cheltuielilor judiciare sau\na amenzii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1473857116\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1271\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1473857116\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)M&#259;surile preventive prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) pot\nfi dispuse pe o perioad&#259; de cel mult 60 de zile, cu posibilitatea\nprelungirii în cursul urm&#259;ririi penale &#351;i a men&#355;inerii în cursul\nprocedurii de camer&#259; preliminar&#259; &#351;i al judec&#259;&#355;ii,\ndac&#259; se men&#355;in temeiurile care au determinat luarea acestora, fiecare\nprelungire neputând dep&#259;&#351;i 60 de zile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1803656546\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1270\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1803656546\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, m&#259;surile\npreventive se dispun de judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i\nlibert&#259;&#355;i prin încheiere motivat&#259; dat&#259; în camera de\nconsiliu, cu citarea persoanei juridice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1930301896\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1269\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1930301896\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Participarea procurorului este obligatorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_605090468\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1268\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_605090468\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Împotriva încheierii se poate face contesta&#355;ie la\njudec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i sau, dup&#259; caz, la\njudec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259; ori instan&#355;a ierarhic\nsuperioar&#259;, de c&#259;tre persoana juridic&#259; &#351;i procuror, în\ntermen de 24 de ore de la pronun&#355;are, pentru cei prezen&#355;i, &#351;i de\nla comunicare, pentru persoana juridic&#259; lips&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1127264499\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1267\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1127264499\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)M&#259;surile preventive se revoc&#259; de c&#259;tre judec&#259;torul\nde drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i la cererea procurorului sau a persoanei\njuridice, iar de c&#259;tre judec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259;\n&#351;i de c&#259;tre instan&#355;&#259; &#351;i din oficiu, numai când se\nconstat&#259; c&#259; nu mai exist&#259; temeiurile care au justificat luarea\nsau men&#355;inerea acestora. Dispozi&#355;iile alin. (5)-(7) se aplic&#259; în\nmod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1041690867\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1266\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1041690867\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Împotriva reprezentantului persoanei juridice sau a\nmandatarului acesteia pot fi luate m&#259;surile prev&#259;zute la art. 265\n&#351;i art. 283 alin. (2), iar fa&#355;&#259; de practicianul în\ninsolven&#355;&#259;, m&#259;sura prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 283 alin. (2).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_486818658\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1265\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_486818658\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Luarea m&#259;surilor preventive nu împiedic&#259;\nluarea m&#259;surilor asigur&#259;torii conform art. 249-256.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}